{"tid":1190768,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【汽油彈事件】從六四看六九之歷史端倪","createTime":"2019-06-07T13:52:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T14:02:20.000Z","uid":101110,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"93bb9a1c55108d2fec9468fa84fcd9c4e67746e5","tid":1190768,"uid":101110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T13:52:02.000Z","msg":"古：1989年時任南華早報中國版記者林和立回顧六四民運背後槍桿子保政權的中共思維、保守元老派節節擊退開明派、鄧小平是忠誠黨員甚於改革者、製造藉口讓戒嚴部隊入城鎮壓人民。（取自：我是記者 我的六四故事 - I am a Journalist, My June 4 story)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今：今日凌晨，香港灣仔警察總部門外一輛警方衝鋒車被狂徒投擲汽油彈。港島總區重案組警司羅國凱對事件予以嚴厲譴責，並強調針對警察的行為絕不姑息。<br />\n（取自：大公文匯全媒體新聞中心供稿)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7H3dBco.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7H3dBco.png&h=7466c9d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q3y5si3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ3y5si3.png&h=2eb6160d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aKb3dY4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaKb3dY4.png&h=112e2dbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n7Dw7i5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn7Dw7i5.png&h=46d1b540&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KBBuTY6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKBBuTY6.png&h=85f20801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p4E8p5N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp4E8p5N.png&h=911d3259&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nbrCiqO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnbrCiqO.png&h=bc864192&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Pm0R9PNzbTk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPm0R9PNzbTk&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8uuF5TOcUp1XGW39uuIwQJ%2Fg%3D&h=b8063fa5\" targ